block content
  .col
    h1 About this website
    p.mt-3 Hi, I am <b>David Rasolondramanitra</b> and I built this website to play around with some technologies.
      |  If you want me to add a feature or if you want to add it yourself, you can leave a comment below
      | or go to my <a href='http://github.com/drasolon'>Github page</a>.
  .col.mt-5
    h3 How was this made ? 
    ul
      li This webapp is a <a href='https://nodejs.org/en/'>Nodejs</a> Application running with <a href='http://expressjs.com/'>Express.js</a>.
      li It runs on a <a href='https://www.ovh.com/com/'>OVH</a> virtual server running Debian.
      li The frontend is styled with <a href='https://getbootstrap.com/'>Bootstrap</a>.
      li The database is <a href='https://www.mongodb.com/'>MongoDB</a> and uses <a href='http://mongoosejs.com/'>Mongoose</a> as an ODM.
  .col.mt-5
    h3 For how long are the games saved ?
    p The games are never deleted.
  .col.mt-5
